{"tid":131982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警隊辛辛苦苦四十年，一夜回到解放前","createTime":"2017-02-23T13:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T15:41:59.000Z","uid":73915,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88aec34bc42bb36e343e74aa17d3ac75ee62c50a","tid":131982,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"本身打人，比人斷正<br />\n又話自己冇打人<br />\n又話比人打果個人唔係果個人<br />\n轉頭又話人聊你<br />\n又話段片睇唔到自己個樣<br />\n又話人地自己整傷<br />\n判埋有罪，判埋刑罰<br />\n諗住件事完左，一筆勾銷<br />\n<br />\n點知，Lo Sir仲衝出黎護短<br />\n就係果次見記者，將警隊踢入深淵<br />\n佢以為可以保持士氣<br />\n實際係外人睇黎，就係不分是非黑白<br />\n<br />\n琴日三萬人圍爐<br />\n爆粗都算，會唔會拎猶太人黎講呀<br />\n宜家重要想上訴<br />\n片都出晒街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藍絲成日話敢做唔敢認，真係有例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25d1fb1c3a43c55f81c8f26eb7d455c2a28c436","tid":131982,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/195824_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F195824_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f063a0b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24393cc6f7c17712207f66e058147b164831dc9","tid":131982,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"多謝警隊提供笑話"},{"pid":"084e21fd741da810ee17902a485f198639c02d6b","tid":131982,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"都好呀<br />\n俾班愛發夢既香港人睇清楚咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然係金魚記憶"},{"pid":"b8fb3bb25e07729882e5fd3353716d4975698979","tid":131982,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2